 />\n贏左就出黎使風使到盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T15:14:24.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"a38680f6e90104d035d280e2549518e8a1fde50f","tid":1744203,"uid":194399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T15:16:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44b97a7a84a567adce4d6e8b7ab59257cd24a5e2","tid":1744203,"uid":182061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T15:16:12.000Z","msg":"票要投，輸咗當睇唔到"},{"pid":"209561d6dab20d049d66ff37a3073a51e2dd5b23","tid":1744203,"uid":104767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"561fa5e9d6257b0f6c160dd347c54ca5ea779f0d","tid":1744203,"uid":226466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T15:13:19.000Z","msg":"屌投撚咗先啦<br />\n<br />\n你投完話之你出返黎搞事"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T15:16:37.000Z","msg":"區選此局獲勝關鍵只有 &lsquo;避免輸左帶嚟嘅惡果&rsquo;。<br />\n冇話唔投，不過輸當睇唔到重要D。<br />\n全部人冇得投最好"},{"pid":"7a0fde7a3915aa732b25174a0fcd661ece9f0834","tid":1744203,"uid":75664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T15:17:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e8d19cc0acfbd6f2b7ebaa752021ebd2f0353c9","tid":1744203,"uid":78186,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T15:17:44.000Z","msg":"其實我都係唔明有咩人打會打咁大篇文去造風向<br />\n仲要係連登？<br />\n做咩姐？"},{"pid":"a25ea6bfea85fa109adcfd6052abc5752d3cef2c","tid":1744203,"uid":78186,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"209561d6dab20d049d66ff37a3073a51e2dd5b23","tid":1744203,"uid":104767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"561fa5e9d6257b0f6c160dd347c54ca5ea779f0d","tid":1744203,"uid":226466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T15:13:19.000Z","msg":"屌投撚咗先啦<br />\n<br />\n你投完話之你出返黎搞事"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T15:16:37.000Z","msg":"區選此局獲勝關鍵只有 &lsquo;避免輸左帶嚟嘅惡果&rsquo;。<br />\n冇話唔投，不過輸當睇唔到重要D。